name: Duplicate transactions
description: If duplicate transactions are in your data, the same data will be evaluated more than once and bias your measurement. The transactionID must be unique for every transaction made on website.

blocks.description: Loads data and checks for presence of transaction data
The test will detect the faulty transactions, which is when one transactionID is associated with multiple transactions
blocks.passMessage: Every transaction ID corresponds to a single transaction.
blocks.failHowtofix: If the percentage of duplicate transactions is high, check if information is sent only on purchase page.
